    "Further details and extended results are provided in the supplementary material.",
    "We include empirical analyses of the multi-scale encoding strategy and the refinement stage.",
    "We report the computational cost of DIVERSEVAR, showing that DIVERSEVAR introduces minimal overhead in runtime.",
    "We also report additional metrics on text-alignment, comparison with prompt-rewriting, and results of varying the CFG weights, sampling temperature, and top-p sampling parameters.",
    "The supplementary also presents additional qualitative results and ablations of the Pareto curves."
